title: Airbnb May Tap Morgan Stanley, Goldman Sachs as It Prepares to Go Public, Sources Say -Reuters
text:
--Airbnb Inc. is expected to hire Morgan Stanley (MS) and Goldman Sachs Group Inc. (GS) to advise as the short-term rental company prepares to go public sometime in 2020, Reuters reported Wednesday, citing "people familiar with the matter."

--Airbnb might go public around the middle of next year, the report said, citing "one of the sources."

--Airbnb, Morgan Stanley and Goldman Sachs declined to comment, the report said.

Full story: https://www.reuters.com/article/us-airbnb-listing-exclusive/exclusive-morgan-stanley-goldman-sachs-poised-to-lead-airbnbs-listing-sources-idUSKBN1WH2JM?il=0
